1 - About
    -----

    вЂњProofcaseвЂќ is a collection of small, self-contained Rocq developments. Each
    component is designed to stand independently, typically serving as a formal
    companion to a paper, note, or conceptual construction.


2 - Style
    -----

    The formalizations prioritize clarity and minimality. Developments follow
    established practices and contemporary conventions, with an emphasis on
    readable structure and disciplined proof design.


3 - Structure
    ---------

