    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ _CoqProject
    в”‚
    в”‚      Rocq project manifest. Declares the logical root, namespace
    в”‚      mappings (-Q), and the complete ordered list of source files
    в”‚      to be compiled.
    в”‚
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ builders
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 1 compile.command
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”‚      Compiles the project into an isolated shadow build under
    в”‚    в”‚      scratch/shadow/, runs axiom discipline checks, and writes
    в”‚    в”‚      a certificate to success.txt on a clean Makefile run.
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 2 print.command
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”‚      Concatenates selected .v files into a single context dump
    в”‚    в”‚      (v.context.txt). Source selection is driven interactively
    в”‚    в”‚      by a _Textslect file or _CoqProject.
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ 3 tree.command
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”‚      Generates a module dependency graph via coqdep. Outputs a
    в”‚    в”‚      .dot graph, edge list, topological sort, and an SVG render
    в”‚    в”‚      into scratch/.
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ _TextslectFLT
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в”‚      A curated file list for selective concatenation. Read by
    в”‚    в”‚      2 print.command to constrain output to a chosen subset of
    в”‚    в”‚      sources, independent of _CoqProject order.
    в”‚    в”‚
    в”‚    в””в”Ђв”Ђ success.txt
    в”‚
    в”‚           Build certificate produced by 1 compile.command. Records
    в”‚           the build timestamp, Rocq version, axiom listing, a
    в”‚           _CoqProject snapshot, and optional per-file hashes.
    в”‚
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ scratch
    в”‚
    в”‚      Ephemeral build workspace. Holds the shadow source tree,
    в”‚      build.log, dependency graph outputs, and concatenation
    в”‚      artifacts. Not formally tracked.
    в”‚
